Barroso Says Forecasts Point to a Strong EU Economic Slowdown

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   S t e a r n s
-- 
2011-09-28T07:34:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/barroso-says-forecasts-point-to-a-strong-eu-economic-slowdown.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said forecasts point to a “strong slowdown” of the
European economy.  “We do not have much room for a new fiscal stimulus,”
Barroso told the European Parliament in Strasbourg,  France ,
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
